00:46:42,730 --> 00:46:45,010
That they could then become
a great civilization.

785
00:46:46,930 --> 00:46:49,970
It was only through destruction
that they could have the polis,

786
00:46:50,050 --> 00:46:51,790
the alphabet, and Homer.

787
00:46:52,010 --> 00:46:54,770
Okay? And that's the main
message of human history.

788
00:46:55,070 --> 00:46:57,250
It's through destruction
